                        "quantity_236": ",SPC"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Absolute intensity.",
                "Pulser calibrated against the 7722-keV double-escape",
                " peak of aluminum, which was determined from the",
                " accurately measured value of the 10834.2-keV line in",
                " nitrogen using BeN(3) sample (F.Everling+,1960).",
                "Relative efficiency for detecting gamma rays as a",
                " function of energy measured by studying capture",
                " spectrum from BeN(3) and comparing it with that",
                " reported in (Bartholomew+,1957)."
              ]
            }
          ],
